!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!
!	SINCE THE BOTTOM OF THE WELL IS NORMALIZED TO -1 (V(XMIN)=-1),
!   BEGINNING WITH AN ENERGY OF -1 (E=-1) ENSURES THE ACTION IS ZERO.
!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!
    PRINT *,'ENTER THE VALUE OF GAMMA:'
